<h2>Minimalist Web Design</h2>
<p><small><span class="entypo-clock"></span> Published on April 8, 2014</small></p>
<p><i>Minimalist design has been described as design at its most basic, stripped of superfluous elements, colors, shapes and textures. Its purpose is to make the content stand out and be the focal point. From a visual standpoint, minimalist design is meant to be calming and to bring the mind down to the basics. </i></p>
<p>Read the article.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://debashisbarman.tumblr.com/post/82093725972/minimalist-web-design">Minimalist Web Design</a></p>
